Package java.lang.classfile.instruction

package java.lang.classfile.instruction
java.lang.classfile.instruction is a preview API of the Java platform.
Programs can only use java.lang.classfile.instruction when preview features are enabled.
Preview features may be removed in a future release, or upgraded to permanent features of the Java platform.

Provides interfaces describing code instructions for the java.lang.classfilePREVIEW library.

The java.lang.classfile.attribute package contains interfaces describing code instructions.
Since:
22
